result.adr_address: 36-38 Ashley Rd, Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong
result.formatted_address: 36-38 Ashley Rd, Tsim Sha Tsui, Hong Kong
result.name: La Taverna Restaurant Italian

reviews.text:
We had a party of 8 people come order several dishes of food to share. There are many things wrong with this place.

False advertising - the but 1 get 1 free pasta is only available PER table, not per couple.

Small portions - none of the dishes could satisfiably feed one person and was horrendously overpriced.

Slow service - each dish came out one at a time every 30 minutes. We ordered 6 dishes and had to wait 2 hours to get all the food. 

No water - If you wanted to drink anything, buy the wine or the coffee, or at least the mineral water that was $60 to start.

Overall this place looks great and the atmosphere is nice but everything inside from the service to the food is terrible.
Very friendly staff that don't intrude but still check in to see how your meal is. High quality food and nice atmosphere

This ltalian restaurant is located here over ten years already. Their Boss is real Italian, so the good is traditional and the atmosphere there is great, you can enjoy an evening with friends or family. l love the ceacer salad, the Palma ham pizza, the mussels are really juicy........  The desserts also yummy, overall is great.
The manager here is amazing! It’s my friend’s birthday and he helped me to arrange one of the best tiramisu cake in HK! Their pizza is a must to order and the vibe is very nice and historical:)
Service is terrific. The food was much better this year, so steps in the right direction, although you shouldn't confuse this with home-style Italian. But worth going for a nice meal and evening.

result.adr_address: 香港尖沙咀亞士厘道36-38號
result.formatted_address: 香港尖沙咀亞士厘道36-38號
result.name: La Taverna

reviews.text:
イタリアン料理食べたいなら、ここはハズレなし。
香港でイタリアン！それなりに価格も覚悟したほうがいいでしょう。
オススメがハムの詰め合わせですが、それなりに量が多いから、三人以上居ないと厳しいかもしれません。
注文は基本的に英語、微妙に日本語ができるけど、期待し過ぎると、店員がてんばってしまうから、いじめ過ぎないように。
金土は予約入れても二時間程度しか居させてくれない、と電話では言うけど、実際はお客さんの入り具合見て長居できる場合もある。
店員のサービスは洗練されてるので気持ちのいい時間を過ごせると思う。
全体的に文句なしの五点満点💯

今晚去左間超正嘅餐廳，服務態度一流。我想試徒拎起碟餸，個服務員就會飛身過來講”對唔住，我招呼不週”!!! 😂😂😂。
XX煮硯(唔記得)，海鮮湯，tiramisu，都係超好味。
👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻👍🏻

睇遇好多食評都話好高水準，一心去試吓，但非常失望，可能手工麵買哂，叫佐牛仔肉醬意大利粉，上枱時份量超小，又過咸，重等佐差不多45分鐘，追佐兩次，當時店内並不多人，真差，沙律就ok，但都係賣曬，我原本叫凱撒沙律，都要轉雜菜，當時都係八點半，好多嘢已經無哂，可能早啲去會好啲，牛朳就平平無奇，無特别驚喜，應該都唔會再去。
